procedures.name: Blood Draw

code.decode: Collection of venous blood by venipuncture

procedures.label: Sampling
procedures.description: Withdrawal of blood for central laboratory testing including HbA1c, C-peptide, and safety labs.

procedures.name: Continuous Glucose Monitoring

code.decode: Ambulatory continuous glucose monitoring of interstitial tissue fluid

procedures.label: CGM
procedures.description: Periodic measurement of interstitial glucose levels using a subcutaneous sensor.

procedures.name: Electrocardiogram

code.decode: Electrocardiogram, routine ECG with at least 12 leads

procedures.label: ECG
procedures.description: Standard safety assessment of cardiac electrical activity.

procedures.name: Physical Examination

code.decode: Periodic comprehensive preventive medicine reevaluation and management

procedures.label: Physical Exam
procedures.description: Assessment of physical findings for safety and tolerability.

procedures.name: Vital Signs
procedures.label: Vitals
procedures.description: Measurement of blood pressure (seated systolic and diastolic) and heart rate.

procedures.name: Self-Monitoring of Blood Glucose

code.decode: Self-measured blood pressure using a device, patient education/training and device calibration

procedures.label: SMBG
procedures.description: 6-point glucose profiles performed by the subject using a meter.

procedures.name: Blood Ketone Testing

code.decode: Acetone or other ketone bodies, serum; quantitative

procedures.label: Ketone Monitoring
procedures.description: Measurement of blood ketones during acute illness or potential DKA symptoms.

procedures.name: Subcutaneous Injection

code.decode: Therapeutic, prophylactic, or diagnostic injection; subcutaneous or intramuscular

procedures.label: Insulin Injection
procedures.description: Administration of basal and prandial insulin via MDI.

procedures.name: Pregnancy Test

code.decode: Urine pregnancy test, by visual color comparison methods

procedures.label: HCG Test
procedures.description: Serum or urine pregnancy test for WOCBP.

medicalDevices.name: Combined Blood Glucose and Ketone Meter
medicalDevices.label: Glucose/Ketone Meter
medicalDevices.description: Handheld device for self-monitoring of glucose and ketones.

medicalDevices.name: Insulin Pump
medicalDevices.label: CSII Pump
medicalDevices.description: Device for continuous subcutaneous insulin infusion.

medicalDevices.label: Subcutaneous Sensor
